item.title: CVE-2023-41840|2024-08-02T19:09:49.203Z -- fortinet -- forticlientwindows
item.description: A untrusted search path vulnerability in Fortinet FortiClientWindows 7.0.9 allows an attacker to perform a DLL Hijack attack via a malicious OpenSSL engine library in the search path.

item.title: CVE-2023-33304|2024-08-02T15:39:36.160Z -- fortinet -- forticlientwindows
item.description: A use of hard-coded credentials vulnerability in Fortinet FortiClient Windows 7.0.0 - 7.0.9 and 7.2.0 - 7.2.1 allows an attacker to bypass system protections via the use of static credentials.
